ous practical services such as arranging accommodations at the nearby hotel Van der Valk Hotel Leiden\/Tulip Inn Leiden at a special rate, visa assistance, and bike rental. For more information see:&nbsp;<a href=\"http:\/\/www.lorentzcenter.nl\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">www.lorentzcenter.nl<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>SOC<\/strong>: Fabio Antonini (chair), Maya Fishbach, Davide Gerosa, Laura Nuttall, Rosalba Perna, Simon Portegies Zwart.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"724\" height=\"1024\" src=\"http:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/challenges-and-future-perspectives-in-gravitational-wave-astronomy-poster-pic-724x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6209\" style=\"width:830px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/challenges-and-future-perspectives-in-gravitational-wave-astronomy-poster-pic-724x1024.jpg 724w, https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/challenges-and-future-perspectives-in-gravitational-wave-astronomy-poster-pic-212x300.jpg 212w, https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/challenges-and-future-perspectives-in-gravitational-wave-astronomy-poster-pic-768x1086.jpg 768w, https:\/\/davidegerosa.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/challenges-and-future-perspectives-in-gravitational-wave-astronomy-poster-pic.jpg 992w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 724px) 100vw, 724px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The workshop \u201cChallenges and future perspectives in gravitational-wave astronomy: O4 and beyond\u201d will take place at the Lorentz Center (Leiden, Netherlands) from